These are Puzzles for 4x7 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 4x7-Level-8-1::.
The people have 7 different hobbies: reading, skydiving, collecting, singing, photography, dancing, puzzles
There are 7 different nationalities: mexican, american, russian, chinese, australian, turkish, nigerian
7 different games are played: domino, poker, monopoly, snooker, mah-jongg, backgammon, bridge
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: skiing, rugby, cricket, lacrosse, basketball, soccer, swimming
 1. the person playing poker is somewhere to the right of the person playing domino##5
 2. the person who's hobby is skydiving is somewhere to the left of the person playing domino##5
 3. the american is somewhere to the left of the person playing backgammon##5
 4. the chinese is on the left or right of the person playing domino##3
 5. the russian is not to the left of the person who's sport is cricket##8
 6. the nigerian is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is dancing##3
 7. the american is not to the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##8
 8. the person playing snooker is not to the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##8
 9. the chinese is not to the left of the person who's sport is skiing##8
10. the person who's hobby is collecting is somewhere between the russian and the person who's sport is skiing##7
11. the person who's hobby is skydiving is not to the left of the chinese##8
12. the person who's hobby is skydiving is somewhere to the left of the australian##5
13. the person who's sport is cricket is not to the left of the person playing mah-jongg##8
14. the person who's hobby is photography is not the person who's sport is skiing##6
15. the person who's hobby is collecting is somewhere to the right of the person playing poker##5
16. the person who's hobby is reading is not to the left of the person playing domino##8
17. the person who's hobby is photography is not to the right of the person who's sport is cricket##8
18. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the left or right of the person who's sport is rugby##3
19. the person who's hobby is skydiving is not to the left of the person who's sport is skiing##8
20. the person playing mah-jongg is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is lacrosse##5
21. the person who's sport is rugby is on the left of the person playing backgammon##1
22. the person who's sport is skiing is not to the right of the person who's hobby is dancing##8
23. the person who's hobby is reading is the person playing mah-jongg##1
24. the person who's hobby is dancing is somewhere to the left of the russian##5
25. the person who's sport is soccer is not to the left of the chinese##8
26. the person playing poker is somewhere to the left of the nigerian##5
27. the person playing bridge is somewhere to the right of the turkish##5
28. the person playing bridge is somewhere between the person playing poker and the russian##7
29. the american is on the right of the chinese##1
30. the person who's sport is cricket is the person who's hobby is dancing##1
31. the person playing domino is on the left or right of the australian##3
32. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the left or right of the person playing mah-jongg##3
33. the person who's hobby is puzzles is not to the left of the person who's sport is swimming##8
34. the person who's hobby is photography is not the person who's sport is soccer##6
35. the mexican is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##5
36. the person who's hobby is skydiving is not to the right of the person who's hobby is dancing##8
37. the nigerian is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is swimming##5
38. the person playing mah-jongg is not to the left of the american##8
39. the nigerian is not the person who's sport is soccer##6
40. the person who's sport is basketball is on the left of the person who's sport is soccer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |   3    |    4     |       5        |       6       |       7       |
