.:: Puzzle 4x7-Level-8-2::.
7 different games are played: snooker, scrabble, poker, whist, domino, monopoly, backgammon
There are 7 different favourite beverages: tea, sprite, juice, almond-milk, fanta, soy-milk, 7up
7 different brands of cigars are smoked: tiparillo, dunhill, chaman, prince, bolivar, davidoff, cain
The people grow 7 different varities of flowers: sunflower, poppy, begonia, balloon-flower, rose, daisy, daffodil
 1. the person drinking tea is somewhere to the left of the person drinking 7up##5
 2. the chaman-smoker is on the left or right of the prince-smoker##3
 3. the person drinking sprite is the person who growsbegonia##1
 4. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the tiparillo-smoker##1
 5. the person who growssunflower is not the person drinking tea##6
 6. the person playing monopoly is somewhere between the person drinking tea and the person who growspoppy##7
 7. the person who growspoppy is somewhere to the right of the person who growssunflower##5
